Free to use - export LinkedIn Sales Navigator contacts into a CSV file. Appends work email addresses where possible. 

This has to be the easiest way to save leads from Sales Navigator. 

HOW TO USE THE DATYLE EXTENSION FOR SALES NAVIGATOR

1. Load the extension.
2. When prompted, enter your email address. This is purely used to send results to.
3. Open LinkedIn Sales Navigator, run your search.
4. Wait around 30-60 minutes to receive the contacts in a CSV file to your email.

Fields included :- 
Name
Job Title
Email
Company
LinkedIn profile URL
Company domain
Company LinkedIn URL
Plus details about the company's tech e.g. whether Salesforce or Hubspot are used, or the email provider they use e.g. Microsoft Outlook 365.

This extension is provided completely free of charge. No card, not even an account is needed. It's so simple!

The Datyle extension ensures that you comply with LinkedIn's rules and restrictions. We prioritize the security of your account.

As standard, you can access 1,800 leads per day for Sales Navigator searches. We recommend extracting no more than this per day but we don't impose any restrictions of our own.

For support or more data appending and contact searching tools visit https://datyle.co

We offer other premium services such as contact finding and job change tracking. Visit https://datyle.co to see more.
